# Cursor Rules for Kromka Project

## Critical Rules

### No Barrel Files
DO NOT create `index.ts` files that re-export from other modules. Import directly from specific files.

```typescript
// ✅ Correct
import { getProducts } from "@/features/products/api/queries";

// ❌ Wrong
import { getProducts } from "@/features/products";
```

### Server/Client Separation
- Server Components by default
- `"use client"` only for event handlers, browser APIs, client state
- `"use server"` for server actions
- `"use cache"` for cached queries

### Feature Module Structure
```
src/features/{name}/
├── api/
│   ├── queries.ts   # "use cache" for public, no cache for admin
│   └── actions.ts   # "use server" with auth guards
├── schema.ts        # Zod validation
└── components/      # Feature-specific components
```

No index.ts re-exports!

